<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="remember-v">remember <strong><em>v</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'membə(r)/    美 /rɪ'membər/  </p>
<p>[通常不用于进行时]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>记得；记住；想起：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I remember my first day at kindergarten very well / clearly.
我清楚地记得第一天上幼儿园的情景。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can’t remember his telephone number.
我想不起他的电话号码了。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>remember doing sth 记得曾做过某事：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I remember meeting her at a party once. 
我记得曾在一次聚会上见过她。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>remember to do sth 记着要做某事：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Remember to turn off the light before you leave. 
走前别忘了关灯。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>remember + (that) / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I remember that there was a beautiful valley near the village. 
我记得村庄附近有个漂亮的山谷。</p><footer>外研③ – 6</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you remember what you said last night? 
你记得自己昨晚说过的话吗？</p><footer>人教⑧ – 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>纪念：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the custom of remembering Jesus’ birth 
纪念耶稣诞生的习俗</p><footer>人教③ – 1</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>代...致意；代...问好：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Will you kindly <strong>remember me to</strong> your family? 
请代我向你的家人问好，好吗?</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-remembered-as-for">be remembered as / for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>因…而著名：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Madame Curie will always be remembered as the discoverer of the element radium. 
居里夫人作为镭元素的发现者将永远被人们记住。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Margaret Mitchell is best remembered for her book, Gone with the Wind. 
玛格丽特·米歇尔因其著作《飘》而著名。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I still remember <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (visit) a friend who’d lived here for fi ve years.  （2018 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. visiting  </p></div>